    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment team reviewed all 13 credibility factors. Seven factors were formally assessed; all seven show achieved levels below required levels for MRL 5. Six factors remain not-assessed, representing significant epistemic gaps. The mesh-independence claim was noted as supporting the discretization error factor assessment; bench-test evidence was reviewed informally during the assessment session but no formal derivation link was established between the claim and any evidence record. On balance, the assessment team accepted the package as complete for submission purposes, noting that the formal credibility decision remains Not Accepted pending resolution of all factor gaps.",
